        <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg card mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold section-title mb-6">Proposed Enhancements</h2>
            
            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">1. Prominent QR Code Scanner</h3>
                <p><strong>Problem:</strong> New users struggle to locate the QR code scanner, causing delays in busy payment scenarios like markets.</p>
                <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Make the QR scanner the default view upon opening the app, with a prominent button or gesture to access it instantly.</p>
                <p class="impact"><strong>Impact:</strong> Reduces payment time, enhancing user experience in high-traffic scenarios.</p>
                <p><strong>Implementation:</strong> Update the appâ€™s homepage UI to prioritize the scanner, with A/B testing to validate user adoption.</p>
                <svg class="representation-img" width="600" height="300" viewBox="0 0 600 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
