            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">2. Personalized Payment Mode</h3>
                <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Users, especially in UPI-dominant markets like India, rarely use all payment options equally, leading to cluttered interfaces.</p>
                <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Introduce a customization feature allowing users to prioritize preferred payment methods (e.g., UPI) on the main screen.</p>
                <p class="impact"><strong>Impact:</strong> Streamlines the payment process, improving user convenience and satisfaction.</p>
                <p><strong>Implementation:</strong> Add a settings module for users to reorder or hide payment options, leveraging user behavior analytics for defaults.</p>
                <svg class="representation-img" width="600" height="300" viewBox="0 0 600 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
