            </div>

            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">3. Fixed Deposit (FD) and Recurring Deposit (RD) Integration</h3>
                <p><strong>Problem:</strong> G-Pay lacks FD/RD investment options, causing users to turn to other platforms for these services.</p>
                <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Integrate FD/RD options within the app, partnering with trusted financial institutions to offer competitive rates.</p>
                <p class="impact"><strong>Impact:</strong> Increases user stickiness, reducing drop-off to competitor apps.</p>
                <p><strong>Implementation:</strong> Develop a secure investment module with clear UX for selecting and managing FD/RD plans.</p>
                <svg class="representation-img" width="600" height="300" viewBox="0 0 600 300" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
