            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">4. Revamped Rewards System</h3>
                <p><strong>Problem:</strong> The current rewards system relies on niche coupons, which lack broad appeal compared to previous cashback offers.</p>
                <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Reintroduce direct incentives like cashback or relevant discounts (e.g., Amazon vouchers, Ola/Uber credits) tailored to user spending patterns.</p>
                <p class="impact"><strong>Impact:</strong> Boosts user engagement and app retention through meaningful rewards.</p>
                <p><strong>Implementation:</strong> Use machine learning to personalize rewards based on transaction history, with a budget-friendly reward structure.</p>
