            </div>

            <div class="mb-8">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-800 mb-3">5. Payment Reminders and Flexible UPI Lite Limits</h3>
                <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Users forget bill payments, and the â‚¹2,000 UPI Lite limit feels restrictive for some transactions.</p>
                <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Implement automated reminders for upcoming bills (e.g., mobile recharges) and allow users to set custom UPI Lite limits within a secure range.</p>
                <p class="impact"><strong>Impact:</strong> Enhances financial management and user convenience, reducing missed payments.</p>
                <p><strong>Implementation:</strong> Integrate a notification system for bill tracking and a settings toggle for UPI Lite limit adjustments, compliant with regulatory guidelines.</p>
